msgstr "Confirmación no válida. Por favor, inicie el desistimiento de nuevo."

#: src/Domain/WithdrawalService.php:178
msgid "Right of withdrawal exercised by the consumer (within the period)."
msgstr ""
"Derecho de desistimiento ejercido por el consumidor (dentro del plazo)."

#: src/Domain/WithdrawalService.php:179
msgid ""
"Right of withdrawal exercised by the consumer — flagged outside the computed "
"period; please verify validity."
msgstr ""
"Derecho de desistimiento ejercido por el consumidor — marcado fuera del "
"período calculado; verifique su validez."

#: src/Domain/WithdrawalService.php:264
msgid ""
"Subscription cancelled automatically following the withdrawal (future "
"renewals stopped). Refund / any pro-rata: handle manually."
msgstr ""
"Suscripción cancelada automáticamente tras el desistimiento (renovaciones "
"futuras detenidas). Reembolso / posible prorrateo: gestiónalo manualmente."

#: src/Domain/WithdrawalService.php:265
msgid ""
"Automatic subscription cancellation could not be completed — please cancel "
