msgstr "Acuse de recibo de desistimiento"

#: src/Mail/WooAckEmail.php:66
msgid ""
"Acknowledgement of receipt sent to the consumer when they withdraw from a "
"contract. This email is legally required (Art. 11a / Art. 54-bis); disabling "
"it here only reverts to a plain built-in template — the acknowledgement is "
"still sent."
msgstr ""
"Acuse de recibo enviado al consumidor cuando desiste de un contrato. Este "
"correo es legalmente obligatorio (Art. 11a / Art. 54-bis); desactivarlo aquí "
"solo revierte a una plantilla integrada básica — el acuse de recibo se sigue "
"enviando."

