#: templates/public/verify-receipt.php:83
msgid ""
"This page confirms that the withdrawal record exists and matches its tamper-"
"evident entry in the immutable log. The evidence hash above is the "
"fingerprint of that entry."
msgstr ""
"Esta página confirma que el registro de desistimiento existe y coincide con "
"su entrada inviolable en el registro inalterable. El hash de la prueba que "
"aparece arriba es la huella digital de esa entrada."

#: templates/public/verify-receipt.php:84
msgid ""
"The withdrawal record could not be matched against the immutable log. Please "
"contact the trader."
msgstr ""
"El registro de desistimiento no ha podido cotejarse con el registro "
"inalterable. Póngase en contacto con el empresario."

